accessibility.text: Welcome to North Myrtle Beach! The weather is absolutely gorgeous for a walk along the beach, or a relaxing soak in the resort hot tub. Nearby Myrtle Beach is abuzz with Food and Fall Festivals, car shows, and  seasonal shopping. Prefer to get in a few rounds of golf? The four acclaimed Barefoot Golf Courses are on site along with restaurants, spa,  and across the waterway, the popular Barefoot Landing! Townhome amenities include a sun room, patio, and mini coffee bar. See you soon!
Luxury Vacation Townhouse at Barefoot Resort - North Myrtle Beach, SC
